{
  "date": "2026-04-02",
  "title": "When God Feels Silent…. What Comes Out?",
  "scriptures": [
    {
      "ref": "Matthew 27:46",
      "text": "My God, My God, why have You forsaken Me?"
    },
    {
      "ref": "John 19:28",
      "text": "I thirst."
    }
  ],
  "sections": [
    {
      "key": "moment_on_the_cross",
      "label": "Moment on the Cross",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "The sky has gone dark.",
            "The crowd is still there….",
            "but heaven feels quiet.",
            "No answer.",
            "No relief.",
            "No rescue.",
            "Just silence."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "prefix": "👉",
          "text": "What comes out of you when God doesn’t respond the way you hoped?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "read_this_out_loud",
      "label": "Read This Out Loud",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Faith is not tested",
            "when God feels close….",
            "It’s tested",
            "when He feels distant."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "devotional",
      "label": "Devotional",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Jesus feels the weight of separation…. And instead of pretending He tells the truth."
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "“My God…. why?”",
            "“I thirst.”",
            "No mask.",
            "No performance.",
            "No pretending."
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bullet_list",
          "items": [
            "Distract instead of deal",
            "Numb instead of name",
            "Perform instead of confess"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "But Jesus?",
            "👉 He stays",
            "👉 He speaks honestly",
            "👉 He doesn’t disconnect"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "reflex_test",
      "label": "Reflex Test",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "bullet_list",
          "items": [
            "God feels distant",
            "Prayers feel unanswered",
            "Life doesn’t make sense"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "👉 Your instinct reveals your formation",
            "Do you drift…. or stay?"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "the_90_second_window",
      "label": "The 90-Second Window",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "prefix": "👉",
          "text": "You have a window to choose truth over impulse."
        },
        {
          "type": "lines",
          "items": [
            "Sit in it.",
            "Don’t escape it."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "shadow_confession",
      "label": "Shadow Confession",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "callout",
          "prefix": "👉",
          "text": "I drift when God feels silent."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "gem",
      "label": "Gem",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "quote",
          "text": "You can’t heal what you won’t acknowledge."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "key": "invitation",
      "label": "1 Invitation",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Tell God the truth tonight."
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "text": "Not the polished version. The real one."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "__insert_block_header": "2026-04-02_matthew-27-46_when-god-feels-silent-what-comes-out|"
}
